div.div: JTL Infra Director Vijay Singla launched CSR to Help the Poor and Needy During the Pandemic

Vijay Singla led JTL Infra Ltd on its CSR activities to help the poor and needy during the coronavirus outbreak. This initiation fed almost 5000 people per day.
